highlights.text: Tobias Sten has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Fy faen du e deili” is the highest at #4.
“The Night We Met” by Lord Huron has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 141 weeks straight.
“DESPUÉS DE LA FERIA” by Ramón is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #42.
“Emotion” by Astrid S is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 126 spots at #70.
